<div id="pf3674" class="pf w5c h236" data-page-no="3674"><div class="pc pc3674 w5c h236"><div class="t mf36 xd0 h3b y2bf4 ff6 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Home—Primary Center of Education </div><div class="t mf8 x86 h1 y2cdd ff1 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 7 </div><div class="t m226 xef h25c y2bf8 ffd fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">❑ </div><div class="t m687 x25 h24 y2b17 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Wednesday </div><div class="t m1755 xba h3b y2bf9 ff6 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">November 10 </div><div class="t m1408 x69 h33 y2183 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;And the sons of the prophets said unto Elisha, Be-</div><div class="t m208a xb h33 y23fb ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hold now, the place where we dwell with thee is too </div><div class="t m7b2 xb h33 y235f ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">strait for us. Let us go, we pray thee, unto Jordan, and </div><div class="t m23c7 xb h33 y230a ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">take thence every man a beam, and let us make us a </div><div class="t m2893 x51 h33 yca5 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">place there, where we may dwell. And he answered, </div><div class="t m9ca xb h33 y3c6 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Go ye.&quot; </div><div class="t m1cd x9b h4 yed9 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In the education of the Israelites, much attention was given </div><div class="t m26d x51 h4 yd90 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to training each child in some practical trade. No matter what </div><div class="t mac5 x51 h4 y834 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">role he might follow in later life, he was always capable of </div><div class="t m168 xb h4 ybcc ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">supporting himself by his hands. </div><div class="t m6b6 x65 h33 y2182 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Part 4 </div><div class="t m80a x4a h33 y2428 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">IMPORTANCE </div><div class="t m10b x5d h33 y211f ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">OF A TRADE </div><div class="t m86 x18 h33 y3c6 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2&apos;Kings 6:1, 2 </div><div class="t m14ac x69 h33 y1097 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What is said about